features: Large Size, Large Capacity - Our back of door storage organizer is made of moisture-proof, breathable, tough, and tasteless environmentally friendly non-woven fabric. It has 5 large pockets of 14.5(L) * 6.5(W) * 6.5(H) inches, and the spacing between each layer of pockets has increased to 4.5 inches. The capacity is enough to hold many items of different sizes, and you can easily put in and take out the items you need. 20KG Weight Capacity, create more extra space for you to the greatest extent.

No More Tilting - The stitched design between the side pocket makes the whole product no more tilting. The front, side and bottom of the hanging bag behind the door are equipped with cardboard, which allows it to maintain its shape well, so that it will not deform or tilt when carrying heavy objects.

Extra 10 Mesh Pockets Design - This Wall Mount Storage features the latest side mesh pocket design. There are 2 mesh pockets of 6.5 (L) * 6.5 (W) inches on each side of the large pocket, which can store lipstick, thermometers, keys, chargers, charging cables, remote controls, glasses and other small objects. It’s easier to store and take out small objects.

PVC Visualization Window - The visible pocket on the front of this hanging bag storage bag allows you to see the contents of each pocket, clearly know the items placed on each layer, and get a clearer view when taking out the items. Better manage your belongings!

Versatile - This door pocket is suitable for children's rooms, storage rooms, offices, laundry rooms, bedrooms, bathrooms, dormitories, etc. toys, diapers, wet wipes, baby towels, socks, etc. It is suitable for child’s room behind the door, or bedroom to store cosmetics, hair dryers, kettles, curling irons. With two provided metal hooks, the foldable organizer can be hung over a door with thickness less than 2.0in.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Efficient and Versatile Hanging Storage Organizer for Home Organization
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the ULG 1 Pack Over Door Organizer with 5 Large Pockets and 10 Mesh Side Pockets, and I must say, this storage organizer has greatly exceeded my expectations. It offers a practical and efficient solution for keeping my home organized, with its ample storage capacity and versatile design.The ULG Over Door Organizer provides a total of 5 large pockets and 10 mesh side pockets, offering plenty of space to store a wide variety of items. From kids' toys and shoes to diapers and everyday essentials, this organizer accommodates a range of belongings. The large pockets are spacious and sturdy, capable of holding multiple items, while the mesh side pockets are perfect for storing smaller items that need visibility and easy access.One of the standout features of this organizer is the clear window design. Each pocket has a clear window, allowing me to quickly identify the contents without having to open or search through every pocket. It saves me time and effort, especially when I need to find specific items in a hurry.The weight capacity of 44 lbs is impressive. It ensures that the organizer can handle heavier items without sagging or losing its shape. I appreciate the sturdy construction and the reinforced stitching, which add to its durability and reliability over time.Installation is a breeze with the over-door design. The organizer comes with durable hooks that fit securely over most standard doors, eliminating the need for drilling or permanent installation. It's a convenient solution for those who prefer not to leave marks or holes on their doors.The versatility of this organizer is another aspect I appreciate. While it's ideal for use on doors, it can also be hung on walls or inside closets, providing flexible storage options to suit different spaces and needs. The neutral grey color and sleek design blend well with various room decors.In terms of quality, the ULG Over Door Organizer is top-notch. The materials used are durable and of high quality, ensuring its longevity even with regular use. The stitching is well-done, and the pockets are securely attached, ensuring that the organizer can withstand daily wear and tear.In conclusion, the ULG 1 Pack Over Door Organizer with 5 Large Pockets and 10 Mesh Side Pockets is a fantastic addition to any home seeking efficient and versatile storage solutions. Its ample storage capacity, clear window design, and sturdy construction make it a practical choice for organizing various items. I highly recommend this organizer for anyone looking to declutter and streamline their living space.Note: This review is based on my personal experience and opinion with the product.
